{
  "texts": [
    "Hybrid and ensemble approaches were also common.",
    "For instance, Kumar et al. [5] and Makridakis, S. et al.",
    "[26] developed hybrid frameworks that combine classical econometric and deep neural components for volatility and investment forecasting.",
    "Similarly, Zhang et al. [16] and Bouteska et al.",
    "[21] reported that ensemble ML methods outperform linear benchmarks in factor pricing and cryptocurrency prediction."
  ]
}